<h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #111;">Welcome to Framefox Connect</h2>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">Hi <%= @user.first_name.presence || 'there' %>,</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">Welcome to Framefox Connect! You've been invited to set up your account.</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">To get started, please click the button below to set your password:</p>
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <%= link_to "Set My Password", @reset_password_url, style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #0f172a; color: white; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;" %>
</div>
<p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; font-size: 14px;">Or copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; word-break: break-all; color: #3b82f6; font-size: 13px;"><%= @reset_password_url %></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">Once you've set your password, you'll be able to sign in at <%= link_to "Framefox Connect", root_url, style: "color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none;" %>.</p>
<p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">If you didn't expect this invitation, please ignore this email.</p>
<p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">
  Best regards,<br>
  The Framefox Team
</p>
